<hymn_number>240</hymn_number>
<title>Kumsawt Gam Ding</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Van Lal nunnem Immanuel gamnuom,
 Ngaiin ka mau ka thil sun nitin in;
 Sietlei pakbang tuoi tienga ka chen nang,
 Aw ka gel chim thei puoi gamlun ding chu.

[V2]
 Kumsawt gam ding ka gelin,
 Sietlei pakbang a tuoi kal ka ngaklah;
 Gam thiengtho tun kal ka ngaklah,
 Phamsate tawh laituol I lenna ding.

[V3]
 2. Simlei ah albang vaiin kap mah leng,
 Van lal nunnem kawm hung tung ngei ing ting
 Naubang kah luonthi ei nul sakin tin,
 Naubang nuiin gamnuom tuol leng tang ka.

[V4]
 3. Lungkham sawl-ang ban na dingla um lo,
 Nuoi simlei hi lungkham nan a dim hi;
 Naubang ei puiin kumsawt pielgal ah,
 Naubang ka kah sawlbang in bang tang ie.

[V5]
 4. Pielgal gamnuom hawih thuong ka tun tieng leh
 Ka Lal nunnem in eina pawm intin
 Damna siktui thiengin ei sil intin,
 Kumsawt guobang hinna chu chang tang ka.</lyrics>
</song>